§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ For $A ∈ 𝗥^{n × n}$ and $x ∈ 𝗥^n$,
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ x^⊤ A x = ∑_{i,j} A_{ij}x_{i}x_{j}, ⦉
    ⦉
    is a quadratic form. ⦉
⦉

§ Under trace ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Observe that $\tr x^⊤ A x = \tr A x x^⊤ = \tr xx^⊤A$. ⦉
⦉

